songs.title: Spiral Static
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Who's ever known
How much to moan and groan
And quiver inside?
He needs to give you
Everything you need
Is it enough?

[Chorus]
You're running out of time
As it grows in your mind
Feel broken inside, you'll feel

[Verse 2]
Sigh, static moans
A storm growing strong
And it's coming my way
Still she gives you everything you need
Is it enough?

[Chorus]
You're running out of time
As it grows in your mind
Feel broken inside, you'll feel

[Outro]
And I'll feel broken inside, you'll feel
